    <h2>TL;DR</h2>

    <p>Perfect library for adding search, sort, filters and flexibility to tables, lists and various HTML elements. Built to be invisible and work on existing HTML.</p>

    <h3>Core idea</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Simple and invisible</li>
      <li>Easy to apply to existing HTML</li>
      <li>No dependencies</li>
      <li>Fast</li>
      <li>Small</li>
      <li>Handle thousands of items</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Features</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Works both lists, tables and almost anything else. E.g. <code>&lt;div></code>,<code>&lt;ul></code>,<code>&lt;table></code>, etc.</li>
      <li>Search <small><a href="/docs/list-api#search">Read more ›</a></small></li>
